  ('dietitian-moex-00204', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關營養篩檢（nutrition screening），下列敘述何者正確？', '["針對成年病人，好的營養篩選工具敏感性（sensitivity）和特一性（specificity）最好要大於 90％", "在營養篩選工具中，營養不良篩檢工具（Malnutrition Screening Tool, MST）的可信度最差", "迷你營養評估（Mini Nutritional Assessment, MNA）屬於營養評估工具，非營養篩選工具", "醫療機構病歷中的營養篩檢紀錄不具法律效力"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7aa83b1fecb3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "65efadb3135a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
