  ('dietitian-moex-00206', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '王同學，170公分，因多年厭食症，體重僅40公斤，目前因車禍入院後，醫師給予鼻胃管灌食，每日 2,200大卡，此時最需要預防下列何種症狀的發生？', '["低血糖", "低血鈉", "低血鈣", "低血磷"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7aa83b1fecb3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "65efadb3135a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00207', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '長期服用抑制胃酸分泌的藥物最容易產生下列何種維生素缺乏症？', '["維生素B 1", "維生素B 2", "維生素B 6", "維生素B 12"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7aa83b1fecb3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "65efadb3135a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00208', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關管灌餵食，下列敘述何者最適當？', '["鼻胃管使用大於三週之後，宜評估使用gastrostomy tube", "餵食管的孔徑單位為French size，號碼越大孔徑越小", "重症病人應優先考慮nasoduodenal tube來建立灌食路徑", "病人經口進食達需要量的75％，仍需同時以胃管來補充不足的25％，以避免營養不良"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7aa83b1fecb3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "65efadb3135a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
