  ('dietitian-moex-00211', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關兒童及青少年肥胖的體重管理，下列何者錯誤？', '["治療目標是達成健康飲食和活動量，而非達到理想體重", "BMI≧85th percentile且有肥胖併發症時，應仔細評估遺傳、內分泌、心理狀況及其併發症", "8歲以上兒童即使BMI≧95th percentile，仍不建議減輕體重", "維生素D缺乏（≦20 ng/mL）與兒童肥胖有相關性"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7aa83b1fecb3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "65efadb3135a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
